author: Jacob Davey
title: Lil Uzi Vert Just Dropped 4 New Tracks & You Can Listen to Them Here
text:
Before his impending album LUV Is Rage 2 is released, Lil Uzi Vert has eased fans’ apprehension by dropping four new songs via his SoundCloud . You can listen to ”Boring Shit,” “LUV Scars K.o,” “XO TOUR Llif3″ and “YSL.” below.




The four tracks are all sounding fire and catch Uzi in an uptempo, upbeat moment ahead of his eagerly anticipated album. The recent SoundCloud follower award-winner invites some of the game’s hottest producers to provide the beats – “LUV Scars K.o,” is concocted by DJ Plugg, TM88 jumps on “XO Tour Llif3″m DP Beats worked on “YSL,” and “Boring Shit” is produced by Honorable Court.
The latter track has a sample and beat that sounds more befitting for someone like Chance The Rapper, but the Philly MC ensures he goes in on the unusual settings of a gospel choir-sampled beat.
Watch his manga-themed video for “P’s & Q’s” below.
